Different types of creating POST Request
----------------------------------------


1. HashMap - refer Eclipse
2. using org.json - json deendency imp - refer code and pom -add json dependency
3. using POJO(Plain old java object) - refer eclipse
4. using an extrenal JSON file - refer Eclipse

How to create own API
-----------------------------------------
Step 1: Node js
npm - node package manager

node --version
npm --version


Step 2: JSON server
npm install -g json-server

Step3: Save one json file
"name.json" - All files

How to start an API
-----------------------------------------
json-server name.json
npx json-server --watch db.json
json-server --watch db.json



















